smoker
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a little pink sweet, size of aspirin, with a musky taste or perfume, perhaps originally meant to take the smell of smoking from the breath. Jane Godfrey notes that the names is still current, and the sweets still available at Woolworths
Origin:[none]
