Quote: `I had a cigarette the other day after school,' I said. ... ` ... we ate all sorts of things to take the smell away, ...' `Chewing gum's best,' said Cliff. `Or Smokers.' 1978 editorial note 190: Tiny, hard, pink, cylindrical scented sweets.
